name: Corporal Misik
Lore: 'Son of a Tatooine diplomat. Stormtrooper. Biker scout. Deadly shot. Develops speeder bike tactics with Sergeant Barich. Hopes for promotion to Emperor''s Demonstration Team.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of any speeder bike he pilots. When firing a Scout Blaster, adds 1 to his total weapon destiny. When with Barich in a battle and piloting or driving a vehicle, may add that vehicle''s maneuver to your total power.',
